    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat your enemies with umbrella action!</h2></strong><br>Raindrop Umbrella is an exploration 2D action game (Metroidvania). In a world where it has been raining for a long time and everything has collapsed and been transformed, you will use mechanical umbrellas created using lost technology to advance your adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/559adb5241150978e7e7cac10330163a.poster.avif?t=1690090449\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/559adb5241150978e7e7cac10330163a.webm?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/559adb5241150978e7e7cac10330163a.mp4?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can learn new skills by defeating bosses and exploring. They will surely help you in your adventures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/9e6a0916a0298c39808563cb8f6f53af.poster.avif?t=1690090449\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/9e6a0916a0298c39808563cb8f6f53af.webm?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/9e6a0916a0298c39808563cb8f6f53af.mp4?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can punch enemies, step on umbrellas and jump up high......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/702ac2b1a49ee08205bed3c29a223d5f.poster.avif?t=1690090449\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/702ac2b1a49ee08205bed3c29a223d5f.webm?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/702ac2b1a49ee08205bed3c29a223d5f.mp4?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/43e1d963e680e1f7ab5b4c9a7773b6ae.poster.avif?t=1690090449\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/43e1d963e680e1f7ab5b4c9a7773b6ae.webm?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2151080/extras/43e1d963e680e1f7ab5b4c9a7773b6ae.mp4?t=1690090449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The protagonist Shizuku sets out for the altar in the sky to check on the whereabouts of his friend Ame, who has gone missing after a certain ritual. Will Shizuku be able to find Ame again and return home?",
